Package tiles

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Tile
    Every world is made up of a grid of tiles, which are the logical placeholders for the world's entities.
    TileFactory
    Factory-type class for creating different types of Tiles.
    World
    Represents any one region of the game's large world.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    TileException
    This Exception is thrown when an invalid action is attempted on a Tile.
